methods.onError:
Notify the handler that the final state of this export failed.

:param resultState: (io.deephaven.proto.backplane.grpc.ExportNotification.State) - the final state of the export
:param errorContext: (java.lang.String) - an identifier to locate the details as to why the export failed
:param dependentExportId: (java.lang.String) - an identifier for the export id of the dependent that caused the failure if
        applicable
